name: GeniiData Genesis Pass
description: GeniiData is an all-in-one Ordinals platform that provides seeking Ordinals alpha, portfolio tracker, and powerful search engine for inscriptions. GeniiData has released Genesis (GeniiData Genesis Pass), the first parent-child inscription collection, to honor the early users for their support. Benefits of being an OG: Enjoy a perpetual 15% discount on GeniiData's inscribe service, first parent-child inscription collection, VIP access to exclusive events.
